<br>
Where this is applicable is situations like when you have very low XP in your current level. You will need a larger &quot;buffer&quot; than non-hybrids to avoid losing a level when you die.  Overall, it doesn't matter because you get more XP back when rezzed than other classes so it all balances out in the end. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=343.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.showNextMessage?topicID=343.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=343.topic&index=0><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/black_default/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.emailToFriend?topicID=343.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.threadControl?topicID=343.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/black_default/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=343.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub59.ezboard.com/feqrangers65329frm3.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=343.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub59.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select na